114
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:44,850
My dad.

115
00:07:48,940 --> 00:07:50,050
I can't see my dad.

116
00:08:12,900 --> 00:08:15,500
So we brought him back.

117
00:08:30,520 --> 00:08:32,230
Sleep as long as you want.

118
00:08:40,409 --> 00:08:42,030
