119
00:08:51,690 --> 00:08:52,560
I'm so hungry.

120
00:08:52,990 --> 00:08:53,860
You're screwed up.

121
00:08:53,900 --> 00:08:55,090
You skipped school three times. You'll be failed for the exam.

122
00:08:55,140 --> 00:08:56,190
I had allergies.

123
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,200
