152
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:39,380
I saw something more troublesome.

153
00:09:40,940 --> 00:09:41,390
Tell me.

154
00:09:41,780 --> 00:09:42,230
What do you want?

155
00:09:43,500 --> 00:09:44,380
Help me.

156
00:09:47,620 --> 00:09:48,280
Not again.

157
00:09:51,830 --> 00:09:52,340
Make a draw.

158
00:09:52,610 --> 00:09:53,460
I'll write whatever you get.

159
00:10:10,450 --> 00:10:11,760
Or tell me what you want me to write.

160
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,110
Just tell me. I'll write it for you.

161
00:10:15,060 --> 00:10:16,000
Really?

162
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:17,550
Go ahead.

163
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:19,850
Please write down

164
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:21,900
