166
00:10:34,890 --> 00:10:36,800
[His name]

167
00:10:46,670 --> 00:10:48,080
Guangyan, how do you write the "yan" in your name?

168
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:48,910
No.

169
00:10:49,340 --> 00:10:50,150
It's not his name.

170
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:50,990
Then whose name is it?

171
00:10:51,370 --> 00:10:52,460
It's his.

172
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:53,250
Whose?

173
00:10:54,610 --> 00:10:56,430
Forget about it. Just tell me the name.

174
00:10:56,860 --> 00:10:57,580
I don't know.

175
00:10:58,400 --> 00:10:59,620
