176
00:11:02,530 --> 00:11:03,400
I don't know.

177
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:04,930
Another one who knows nothing.

178
00:11:07,100 --> 00:11:07,900
What are you doing?

179
00:11:08,190 --> 00:11:09,170
Are you kidding me?

180
00:11:09,590 --> 00:11:10,750
Who are you talking to?

181
00:11:10,990 --> 00:11:13,020
Explain to me what was going on with this.

182
00:11:13,040 --> 00:11:13,730
So annoying.

183
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:14,970
Don't take this as a treasure.

184
00:11:15,490 --> 00:11:17,040
Didn't you see there's a bunch of them on that woman's head?

185
00:11:17,760 --> 00:11:18,480
What woman?

186
00:11:18,500 --> 00:11:19,220
What does she look like?

187
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:21,510
She has long hair.

188
00:11:21,900 --> 00:11:23,600
Dressed like Dongfang Bubai in the novel.

189
00:11:23,890 --> 00:11:25,440
Always lying on a plant.

190
00:11:25,590 --> 00:11:27,120
You really don't know many vocabularies to describe her.

191
00:12:31,270 --> 00:12:31,740
What are you doing?

192
00:12:32,380 --> 00:12:33,030
You wanted to see her.

193
00:12:33,380 --> 00:12:33,940
Now here she is.

194
00:12:39,240 --> 00:12:39,790
You saw her?

195
00:12:40,670 --> 00:12:41,560
What did you do to me?

196
00:12:42,250 --> 00:12:43,400
-I just drew... -Stress.

197
00:12:43,680 --> 00:12:44,740
My dad lost his job in late middle age.

198
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:45,640
So we had to move in

199
00:12:45,640 --> 00:12:46,810
with an elder lady who remembers nothing

200
00:12:46,810 --> 00:12:48,430
but drinking.

201
00:12:48,520 --> 00:12:49,220
And you are the last straw.

202
00:12:49,260 --> 00:12:50,790
We met you, a loser and scumbag

203
00:12:50,820 --> 00:12:51,680
who lives right next door.

204
00:12:51,680 --> 00:12:53,600
All these made me mentally stressed, which caused my illusion.

205
00:12:54,280 --> 00:12:54,850
What illusion?

206
00:12:55,710 --> 00:12:56,790
You're like when you were in high school.

207
00:12:56,830 --> 00:12:57,920
Really annoying.

208
00:13:10,830 --> 00:13:11,490
Did you hear that?

209
00:13:11,780 --> 00:13:12,840
I'm just a scumbag.

210
00:13:13,260 --> 00:13:14,220
I can't help you.

211
00:13:21,100 --> 00:13:21,910
What do you think, senior?

212
00:13:23,640 --> 00:13:25,420
Indeed, someone who does calligraphy carries a different aura.

213
00:13:41,070 --> 00:13:43,510
Are you coming down or not?

214
00:13:46,970 --> 00:13:50,780
If you don't, I'll stick you inside the case.

215
00:13:53,910 --> 00:13:54,660
Yes, senior.

216
00:13:55,650 --> 00:13:57,710
My friend was born in a calligraphy classroom.

217
00:13:57,750 --> 00:13:58,620
His grandfather was his mentor.

218
00:13:59,460 --> 00:14:01,540
A disciple from a famous calligraphy family.

219
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:03,560
Yeah, that's kinda the story.

220
00:14:04,140 --> 00:14:04,620
Senior.

221
00:14:05,190 --> 00:14:06,380
I was just asking.

222
00:14:07,110 --> 00:14:07,680
Will his performance

223
00:14:07,710 --> 00:14:09,320
affect my probation result?

224
00:14:10,040 --> 00:14:11,280
I'll take you to the water slide

225
00:14:11,300 --> 00:14:12,280
and swimming pool later.

226
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,060
Almost...

227
00:14:20,260 --> 00:14:20,920
What are you doing here?

228
00:14:24,060 --> 00:14:24,870
Help me.

229
00:14:26,740 --> 00:14:28,790
What's wrong with you? Why are you following me?

230
00:14:33,370 --> 00:14:35,550
Please help me to find out about his name.

231
00:14:36,420 --> 00:14:37,620
I said I don't know.

232
00:14:38,370 --> 00:14:39,170
I don't have time to help you.

233
00:14:39,570 --> 00:14:39,960
Just leave.

234
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:43,320
It's no use staring at me like that.

235
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:44,910
Another dead person who couldn't rest in peace

236
00:14:44,930 --> 00:14:45,570
did that to me already.

237
00:14:54,170 --> 00:14:54,950
Okay, whatever.

238
00:14:55,860 --> 00:14:57,110
You'd better just stay here.

239
00:14:57,580 --> 00:14:59,460
You can play with the lights and shake the customers' bed.

240
00:14:59,570 --> 00:15:01,080
Or you can comb your hair in front of the mirror.

241
00:15:01,920 --> 00:15:03,300
This place really suits you.

242
00:15:05,450 --> 00:15:06,150
Whatever.

243
00:15:09,680 --> 00:15:10,730
Sorry, you can come in now.

244
00:15:32,070 --> 00:15:33,680
You said I was just like when I was in high school, didn't you?

245
00:15:34,970 --> 00:15:36,270
I lost my job anyway.

246
00:15:36,350 --> 00:15:37,580
I'll go to your school every day starting tomorrow

247
00:15:37,610 --> 00:15:38,930
