249
00:15:44,180 --> 00:15:45,050
I want to help that woman.

250
00:15:45,200 --> 00:15:45,770
With you.

251
00:15:46,690 --> 00:15:48,220
I told you I had an illusion.

252
00:15:48,490 --> 00:15:49,440
It's none of my business.

253
00:15:50,890 --> 00:15:51,860
Since it's your illusion,

254
00:15:51,880 --> 00:15:53,160
why does she keep showing up in front of me?

255
00:15:54,050 --> 00:15:54,900
You brought her back.

256
00:15:55,090 --> 00:15:55,930
Let's deal with her together.

257
00:15:56,830 --> 00:15:58,490
And you'll have to pay me the compensation for being unemployed.

258
00:15:58,700 --> 00:15:59,470
What compensation?

259
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:00,160
I'm hungry.

260
00:16:01,110 --> 00:16:01,810
Let's go to your dad's place for some noodles.

261
00:16:22,420 --> 00:16:22,890
Why?

262
00:16:23,610 --> 00:16:24,610
Does it embarrass you

263
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:25,520
to walk with me?

264
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:30,360
At least take off your hat.

265
00:16:30,850 --> 00:16:31,820
This suit costs more than 2,000 yuan.

266
00:16:31,840 --> 00:16:32,620
I can't refund it.

267
00:16:32,950 --> 00:16:33,620
So I have to wear it more.

268
00:16:35,130 --> 00:16:35,570
Oh, right.

269
00:16:36,060 --> 00:16:37,080
You'll have to pay for this too.

270
00:16:42,190 --> 00:16:43,500
More than 2,000 yuan? How much more?

271
00:16:45,320 --> 00:16:45,760
I forgot.

272
00:16:46,150 --> 00:16:46,910
29,999.

273
00:16:49,070 --> 00:16:49,460
No.

274
00:16:50,310 --> 00:16:50,930
Three thousand.

275
00:17:13,819 --> 00:17:15,400
Do you remember the career planning class?

276
00:17:17,500 --> 00:17:19,109
What did you fill in that form?

277
00:17:19,810 --> 00:17:20,430
Doctor.

278
00:17:24,730 --> 00:17:25,819
You did turn into a doctor.

279
00:17:27,849 --> 00:17:28,569
All right, let's go.

280
00:17:31,740 --> 00:17:33,870
This is the place where we first found the withered leaves.

281
00:17:32,380 --> 00:17:33,930
[Laboratory Building]

282
00:17:35,130 --> 00:17:35,670
Senior.

283
00:17:37,540 --> 00:17:38,890
